_priceUSD(address,uint256).details: Returns the total price in 18 digit USD for a given asset.

_priceUSD(address,uint256,uint256).details: Returns the total price in USD converting from one scale to another.

params._addr: Address of the strategy to add
params._targetPercent: Target percentage of asset allocation to strategy

changeGovernor(address).details: Transfers Governance of the contract to a new account (`newGovernor`). Can only be called by the current Governor.

governor().details: Returns the address of the current Governor.

isGovernor().details: Returns true if the caller is the current Governor.

isSupportedAsset(address).details: Determines if an asset is supported by the vault.

params._amount: Amount of the asset being deposited
params._asset: Address of the asset being deposited
Address of the asset being withdrawn

transferToken(address,uint256).details: Transfer token to governor. Intended for recovering tokens stuck in     strategy contracts, i.e. mistaken sends.

params._amount: Amount of the asset to transfer

addStrategy(address,uint256).notice: Add a strategy to the Vault.

allocate().notice: Allocate unallocated funds on Vault to strategies.*

getRedeemFeeBps().notice: Get the percentage fee to be charged for a redeem.

isDepositPaused().notice: Getter to check deposit paused flag.

isRebasePaused().notice: Getter to check the rebase paused flag.

mint(address,uint256).notice: Deposit a supported asset and mint OUSD.

mintMultiple(address[],uint256[]).notice: Mint for multiple assets in the same call.

pauseDeposits().notice: Set the deposit paused flag to true to prevent deposits.

pauseRebase().notice: Set the deposit paused flag to true to prevent rebasing.

rebase().notice: Calculate the total value of assets held by the Vault and all        strategies and update the supply of oUsd*

redeem(address,uint256).notice: Withdraw a supported asset and burn OUSD.

setRedeemFeeBps(uint256).notice: Set a fee in basis points to be charged for a redeem.

supportAsset(address,string).notice: Add a supported asset to the contract, i.e. one that can be        to mint OUSD.

totalValue().notice: Determine the total value of assets held by the vault and its        strategies.

unpauseDeposits().notice: Set the deposit paused flag to false to enable deposits.

unpauseRebase().notice: Set the deposit paused flag to true to allow rebasing.
